         <entry xml:id="DRMorrisonetal_ScalpayDRMorrisonmisc10-idp119984752">
            <form>
               <orth>pios</orth>
            </form>
            <def>also bite, portion. Pios is ìm – butter and bread [sic]. [NOTES: the slip has ‘pìos’ and it only gives the meaning of the word in the phrase ‘Pìos is ìm’ – ‘Bread and butter.’]</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="DRMorrisonetal_ScalpayDRMorrisonmisc10-idp119974744">
            <form>
               <orth>tioma-taisein</orth>
            </form>
