            <form>
               <orth>mialagan-mara</orth>
            </form>
            <def>could this be sea-mews, if there is such an English word. Yes – the word meaning to this effect. [NOTES: slipped under ‘mialag-mara’ with pl. mialagan-mara. Definition: Sea-mews (?).]</def>
         </entry>
